url=3D"https://confluence.srv.westpac.com.au">Colin Yau</a> <a class=3D"con=
fluence-userlink user-mention" data-username=3D"L183776" href=3D"/display/~=
L183776" data-linked-resource-id=3D"1296370911" data-linked-resource-versio=
n=3D"1" data-linked-resource-type=3D"userinfo" data-base-url=3D"https://con=
fluence.srv.westpac.com.au">Muthukrishnan Ramaswamy</a> <a class=3D"conflue=
nce-userlink user-mention" data-username=3D"M062280" href=3D"/display/~M062=
280" data-linked-resource-id=3D"1296375477" data-linked-resource-version=3D=
"2" data-linked-resource-type=3D"userinfo" data-base-url=3D"https://conflue=
nce.srv.westpac.com.au">Tejas Koteswara Rao</a> please let me know if the a=
bove is not the case and we can supplement with RTGS specific field.</p>
<p><br></p>
<p><span style=3D"color: rgb(255,0,0);"><strong>Updates:</strong></span></p=
>
<ul style=3D"list-style-type: square;">
<li>Fields that are enriched by PIO will not be sent by Channel.&nbsp;</li>
<li>Fields that are not required by RTGS ( not marked as Yes ) will not be =
sent by Channel.</li>
<li>Refer to the below:</li>
<li><a href=3D"/display/ARTC/W1+Customer+Channel+-+High+Level+SD">W1 Custom=
er Channel - High Level SD</a></li>
</ul>
</div></td>
